<subSubSection id="C337088DF768B129B182FCE033754753" pageId="29" pageNumber="550" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F768B129B182FCE033754753" blockId="29.[151,1437,330,1041]" pageId="29" pageNumber="550">
COMMENTS: Collected on the same day as the type of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F768B129B25AFCE031DF407B" authorityName="Sundevall" authorityYear="1850" box="[799,998,799,825]" class="Aves" family="Alaudidae" genus="Alauda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="29" pageNumber="550" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fasciolata">
<emphasis id="B9598714F768B129B25AFCE031DF407B" box="[799,998,799,825]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="550">Alauda fasciolata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see above). The type locality is probably just south of Potchefstroom. Since this name was shown to be a homonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F768B129B51CFCBC32E340C3" authority="(Latham, 1801)" baseAuthorityName="Latham" baseAuthorityYear="1801" class="Aves" family="Zosteropidae" genus="Zosterops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="29" pageNumber="550" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="lateralis">
<emphasis id="B9598714F768B129B51CFCBC3714401F" box="[1113,1325,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="550">Zosterops lateralis</emphasis>
(Latham, 1801)
</taxonomicName>
, a species from 
<collectingCountry id="F33A1B96F768B129B0D7FC9833C040C3" box="[402,505,871,897]" name="Australia" pageId="29" pageNumber="550">Australia</collectingCountry>
and neighboring islands, Hartlaub created a substitute name, 
<taxonomicName id="4C2D2085F768B129B5F1FC9833B240E7" authority="(Hartlaub 1865: 8 - 9)" baseAuthorityName="Hartlaub" baseAuthorityPageNumber="8 - 9" baseAuthorityYear="1865" class="Aves" family="Zosteropidae" genus="Zosterops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="29" pageNumber="550" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="sundevalli">
<emphasis id="B9598714F768B129B5F1FC9837A540C3" box="[1204,1436,871,897]" italics="true" pageId="29" pageNumber="550">Zosterops sundevalli</emphasis>
(
